metadata.name: PANATA
metadata.description:
"The youth is the hope of the nation" - Rizal

But the current situation seems to indicate that Rizal's message for now is just a question. "Is the youth really the hope of the nation"?

Rizal's "Panata" directs to the Filipino people, especially to our youth today, the appreciation of the country's culture, the society in which he/she was born and the family in which he/she was raised.
"Panata" is a patriotic sentiment and commitment that is ready to face the challenges of times, unity in the development of every Filipino people and love for the country.

Panata by jemuyii
